QuestData.Title: Zanchuli Disbanded
QuestData.Description: I would like to say we are doing well, but we are not.$b$bDe Zanchuli Council is broken. Raal and I are all dat remain who are still loyal to King Rastakhan. You best bring news to your Horde and tell dem what transpired here.$b$bRaal and I will rally what support we can and head for de Zocalo.$b$bAnd hero, thank you for saving my life and my loa.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Baine Bloodhoof in Dazar'alor.
